/-- **GFA-interior analytic-At disk is automatically compatible with
the GFA disk.** Lifted directly from the regular-At version through
the unchanged underlying `F = aperyGFAReal`. -/
lemma aperyGFAInteriorAnalyticDiskAt_compatible_with_GFA
    (center : ℝ) (h_pos : 0 < center) (h_lt : center < 1 / 64)
