/-- **`sSup` of `some.F` on `Icc a b` ≤ `sSup` on `Icc a b'`
when `0 ≤ a ≤ b ≤ b' ≤ 1/64`.** -/
lemma HasAperyAnalyticExtension.sSup_some_F_image_Icc_a_b_le_a_b'
    (h : HasAperyAnalyticExtension)
