/-- **`sInf` of `some.F` on `Icc a b` ≤ `sInf` on `Icc a' b`
when `0 ≤ a ≤ a' ≤ b ≤ 1/64`.** -/
lemma HasAperyAnalyticExtension.sInf_some_F_image_Icc_a_b_le_a'_b
    (h : HasAperyAnalyticExtension)
